---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CyberpunkHero from "../components/CyberpunkHero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="云飞 - 夜城索引"
  description="一个雨夜赛博城市氛围的个人网站首页。"
>
  <main class="page-shell">
    <CyberpunkHero />

    <section class="surface-brief" aria-label="当前网站状态">
      <div class="brief-track">
        <div>
          <span>状态</span>
          <strong>开放实验中</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>技术</span>
          <strong>静态框架 / 样式系统 / 动效</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>节奏</span>
          <strong>夜间构建</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>信号</span>
          <strong>安静系统</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="content-section about-section">
      <div class="section-shell about-grid">
        <div class="section-copy">
          <p class="section-label">关于 / 低光练习</p>
          <h2>在潮湿的夜色里，搭建安静的数字房间。</h2>
          <p>
            我设计并构建个人工具、视觉系统和小型网页产品，关注氛围、克制感和清晰的交互。
          </p>
          <p>
            工作介于代码和视觉方向之间：足够清楚，可以发布；足够安静，可以长期使用；细节足够明确，能让人感到它经过选择。
          </p>

          <div class="process-strip" aria-label="工作流程">
            <span>观察</span>
            <span>原型</span>
            <span>打磨</span>
          </div>

          <div class="tool-cloud" aria-label="偏好的工具和方向">
            <span>静态页面</span>
            <span>样式架构</span>
            <span>交互细节</span>
            <span>图像方向</span>
            <span>氛围系统</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="profile-stack" aria-label="个人信号">
          <div class="profile-visual" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="profile-core"></span>
            <span class="profile-ring profile-ring-a"></span>
            <span class="profile-ring profile-ring-b"></span>
          </div>

          <div class="signal-panel">
            <div class="signal-row">
              <span>关注</span>
              <strong>界面系统</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="signal-row">
              <span>模式</span>
              <strong>设计 / 前端</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="signal-row">
              <span>色调</span>
              <strong>冷玻璃 / 低亮霓虹</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="signal-row">
              <span>当前</span>
              <strong>个人网页实验</strong>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="availability-card">
            <span>可合作方向</span>
            <strong>小型产品 / 个人工具 / 视觉系统</strong>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="works" class="content-section works-section">
      <div class="section-shell">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-label">作品 / 近期信号</p>
          <h2>一些正在成形的构建和视觉练习。</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="works-grid">
          <article class="work-card work-card-large">
            <div class="work-visual work-visual-a" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="work-meta">
              <p class="work-index">01 / 已上线</p>
              <span>首页</span>
            </div>
            <h3>屋顶残影</h3>
            <p>雨夜首页系统，包含分层城市贴图、轻微视差、雾气和克制动效。</p>
            <div class="work-tags">
              <span>首页方向</span>
              <span>轻量素材</span>
              <span>动效</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="work-card">
            <div class="work-visual work-visual-b" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="work-meta">
              <p class="work-index">02 / 草稿</p>
              <span>归档</span>
            </div>
            <h3>信号档案</h3>
            <p>用于整理笔记、参考、碎片想法和项目记录的紧凑型索引。</p>
            <div class="work-tags">
              <span>笔记</span>
              <span>索引</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="work-card">
            <div class="work-visual work-visual-c" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="work-meta">
              <p class="work-index">03 / 练习</p>
              <span>工具</span>
            </div>
            <h3>安静控制台</h3>
            <p>个人仪表盘方向：低对比面板、有用状态信息、减少不必要的视觉噪声。</p>
            <div class="work-tags">
              <span>面板</span>
              <span>系统</span>
            </div>
          </article>

        </div>

        <div class="works-note">
          <span>方向</span>
          <p>
            作品区刻意保持收窄：项目更少，氛围更强，状态更清楚。它应该像一个小型档案，而不是营销网格。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="blog" class="content-section blog-section">
      <div class="section-shell blog-layout">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-label">日志 / 现场笔记</p>
          <h2>来自夜班时间的小段记录。</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="post-list">
          <article class="post-row">
            <time datetime="2026-05-29">2026.05.29</time>
            <div>
              <p class="post-tag">动效</p>
              <h3>多少动效才算刚好？</h3>
              <p>视差应该让层次更容易被读懂，而不是把页面变成游戏登录界面。</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-row">
            <time datetime="2026-05-28">2026.05.28</time>
            <div>
              <p class="post-tag">过程</p>
              <h3>参考图不是背景图</h3>
              <p>用情绪板确定结构，再用清晰、可维护的素材重新搭建场景。</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-row">
            <time datetime="2026-05-25">2026.05.25</time>
            <div>
              <p class="post-tag">色彩</p>
              <h3>冷色城市里的暖色窗光</h3>
              <p>少量暖黄色灯光可以让蓝黑城市显得有人居住，同时不破坏整体暗调。</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <aside class="reading-card" aria-label="写作方向">
          <span>写作节奏</span>
          <p>短篇现场笔记，记录界面品味、参考资料、素材方向，以及视觉噪声的代价。</p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="content-section contact-section">
      <div class="section-shell contact-grid">
        <div class="section-copy">
          <p class="section-label">联系 / 开放频道</p>
          <h2>适合安静产品、视觉系统和网页实验。</h2>
          <p>
            如果你想做一个氛围明确、界面清楚、装饰更少的东西，可以发来一段简短信号。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-panel">
          <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">
            邮箱暂未公开
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/524290569-debug" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            代码仓库 / 524290569-debug
          </a>
          <a href="#home">回到屋顶</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <span>云飞 / 夜城索引</span>
        <span>东八区 / 静态页面构建</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
